<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ( hạfrḥ wạhtf bạlʿwd wạtdẖkr lḥn dạwd )2
 ( ngẖmạt trjʿ wtʿwd mʿ lmsẗ rwḥk lynạ )2
 2- ( ạ̉frḥ wạlqlb sʿyd dh slạm mn ʿndh ạ̉kyd )2
 ( ạ̉yạm klhạ tmjyd fy yswʿnạ ạlgẖạly ʿlynạ )2
 3- ( kẖlṣny wfk qywdy ạ̉htf wạnsẖd ʿly̱ ʿwdy )2
 ( yạ kẖṭyẗ mạʿwdty tswdy nʿmẗ yswʿ tḥmynạ )2
 4- ( bạldf ạ̉nạ wạlmzmạr wrbạb bʿsẖr ạ̉wtạr )2
 ( hạnrnm lw fy ạlnạr wnqwl mjdạaⁿ yạ fạdynạ )2
 5- ( hạtldẖdẖ wạfrḥ byk wḥmwly sạybhạ ʿlyk )2
 ( dh kfạyẗ nrnm lyk fy rḍạh ạlbrkẗ ʿlynạ )2
 6- ( wbṣwty wḥty̱ skạty tsbyḥk ymlạ ḥyạty )2
 ( ạ̉wqạty wkl sʿạty msẖtạq lk ạ̹nt tjynạ )2
 ( hạfrḥ wạhtf bạlʿwd wạtdẖkr lḥn dạwd )2
 ( ngẖmạt trjʿ wtʿwd mʿ lmsẗ rwḥk lynạ )2</lyrics>
<title>hạfrḥ wạhtf bạlʿwd</title>
</song>